{"ID":"20220906204218-nqeeeph","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906204218-nqeeeph","title":"h-0读写分离和分库分表","type":"doc","updated":"20220906204218"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204219-tgu8mc8","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20220906204219-tgu8mc8","updated":"20220906204219"}},{"ID":"20220906204220-njatird","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204220-njatird","updated":"20220906204220"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8. 高性能","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204221-ykhmj97","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906204221-ykhmj97","updated":"20220906204221"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906204222-f6c4lkt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204222-f6c4lkt","updated":"20220906204222"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/","TextMarkTextContent":"JavaGuide"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：「Java学习+面试指南」一份涵盖大部分 Java 程序员所需要掌握的核心知识。准备 Java 面试，首选 JavaGuide！","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204223-59hmvzo","Type":"NodeHTMLBlock","Data":"\u003cdiv align=\"center\"\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://www.yuque.com/docs/share/8a30ffb5-83f3-40f9-baf9-38de68b906dc\"\u003e\n            \u003cimg src=\"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/xingqiu/xingqiu.png\" style=\"margin: 0 auto; width: 850px;\" /\u003e\n        \u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003cp\u003e\n        \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/Snailclimb/JavaGuide-Interview\"\u003eGithub\u003c/a\u003e |\n        \u003ca href=\"https://gitee.com/SnailClimb/JavaGuide-Interview\"\u003eGitee\u003c/a\u003e\n    \u003c/p\u003e  \n\u003c/div\u003e","HtmlBlockType":6,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204223-59hmvzo","updated":"20220906204223"}},{"ID":"20220906204224-nzahodu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204224-nzahodu","updated":"20220906204224"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"8.1 数据库读写分离和分库分表","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204225-xbdt3eg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204225-xbdt3eg","updated":"20220906204225"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相信很多小伙伴们对于这两个概念已经比较熟悉了，这篇文章全程都是大白话的形式，希望能够给你带来不一样的感受。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204226-acsxo0d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204226-acsxo0d","updated":"20220906204226"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果你之前不太了解这两个概念，那我建议你搞懂之后，可以把自己对于读写分离以及分库分表的理解讲给你的同事/朋友听听。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204227-ygkl6lo","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204227-ygkl6lo","updated":"20220906204227"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读写分离","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204228-pmm0gbz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204228-pmm0gbz","updated":"20220906204228"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何为读写分离？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204229-6383lkk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204229-6383lkk","updated":"20220906204229"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"见名思意，根据读写分离的名字，我们就可以知道：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"读写分离主要是为了将对数据库的读写操作分散到不同的数据库节点上。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 这样的话，就能够小幅提升写性能，大幅提升读性能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204230-6eox6df","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204230-6eox6df","updated":"20220906204230"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我简单画了一张图来帮助不太清楚读写分离的小伙伴理解。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204231-h41qaym","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204231-h41qaym","updated":"20220906204231"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"读写分离示意图","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/high-performance/read-and-write-separation-and-library-subtable/read-and-write-separation.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204232-9rjtgmy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204232-9rjtgmy","updated":"20220906204232"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一般情况下，我们都会选择一主多从，也就是一台主数据库负责写，其他的从数据库负责读。主库和从库之间会进行数据同步，以保证从库中数据的准确性。这样的架构实现起来比较简单，并且也符合系统的写少读多的特点。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204233-zz5fsnu","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204233-zz5fsnu","updated":"20220906204233"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读写分离会带来什么问题？如何解决？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204234-u061lx8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204234-u061lx8","updated":"20220906204234"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读写分离对于提升数据库的并发非常有效，但是，同时也会引来一个问题：主库和从库的数据存在延迟，比如你写完主库之后，主库的数据同步到从库是需要时间的，这个时间差就导致了主库和从库的数据不一致性问题。这也就是我们经常说的 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"主从同步延迟"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204235-bkldeqe","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204235-bkldeqe","updated":"20220906204235"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主从同步延迟问题的解决，没有特别好的一种方案（可能是我太菜了，欢迎评论区补充）。你可以根据自己的业务场景，参考一下下面几种解决办法。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204236-xp8m5i7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204236-xp8m5i7","updated":"20220906204236"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1.强制将读请求路由到主库处理。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204237-6qsgul7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204237-6qsgul7","updated":"20220906204237"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"既然你从库的数据过期了，那我就直接从主库读取嘛！这种方案虽然会增加主库的压力，但是，实现起来比较简单，也是我了解到的使用最多的一种方式。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204238-rk5l2gn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204238-rk5l2gn","updated":"20220906204238"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比如 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Sharding-JDBC"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 就是采用的这种方案。通过使用 Sharding-JDBC 的 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"HintManager"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 分片键值管理器，我们可以强制使用主库。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204239-nm7qai0","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":"YGBg","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","CodeBlockCloseFence":"YGBg","Properties":{"id":"20220906204239-nm7qai0","updated":"20220906204239"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"amF2YQ==","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"HintManager hintManager = HintManager.getInstance();\nhintManager.setMasterRouteOnly();\n// 继续JDBC操作\n","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204240-b19a3s3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204240-b19a3s3","updated":"20220906204240"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对于这种方案，你可以将那些必须获取最新数据的读请求都交给主库处理。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204241-b8dh4n9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204241-b8dh4n9","updated":"20220906204241"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"2.延迟读取。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204242-v0wb7pl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204242-v0wb7pl","updated":"20220906204242"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"还有一些朋友肯定会想既然主从同步存在延迟，那我就在延迟之后读取啊，比如主从同步延迟 0.5s,那我就 1s 之后再读取数据。这样多方便啊！方便是方便，但是也很扯淡。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204243-lf4ktnl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204243-lf4ktnl","updated":"20220906204243"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不过，如果你是这样设计业务流程就会好很多：对于一些对数据比较敏感的场景，你可以在完成写请求之后，避免立即进行请求操作。比如你支付成功之后，跳转到一个支付成功的页面，当你点击返回之后才返回自己的账户。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204244-n8ahm71","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204244-n8ahm71","updated":"20220906204244"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://time.geekbang.org/column/intro/100020801?code=ieY8HeRSlDsFbuRtggbBQGxdTh-1jMASqEIeqzHAKrI%3D","TextMarkTextContent":"《MySQL 实战 45 讲》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这个专栏中的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://time.geekbang.org/column/article/77636","TextMarkTextContent":"《读写分离有哪些坑？》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这篇文章还介绍了很多其他比较实际的解决办法，感兴趣的小伙伴可以自行研究一下。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204245-ygtv8xb","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204245-ygtv8xb","updated":"20220906204245"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何实现读写分离？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204246-it5q08a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204246-it5q08a","updated":"20220906204246"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不论是使用哪一种读写分离具体的实现方案，想要实现读写分离一般包含如下几步：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204247-85nz1ki","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204247-85nz1ki","updated":"20220906204247"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204248-y9jfpxj","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204248-y9jfpxj","updated":"20220906204248"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204249-aet2s2y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204249-aet2s2y","updated":"20220906204249"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"部署多台数据库，选择其中的一台作为主数据库，其他的一台或者多台作为从数据库。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204250-bxsxjpl","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204250-bxsxjpl","updated":"20220906204250"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204251-667g7w9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204251-667g7w9","updated":"20220906204251"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"保证主数据库和从数据库之间的数据是实时同步的，这个过程也就是我们常说的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"主从复制"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204252-896ctkw","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204252-896ctkw","updated":"20220906204252"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204253-z2q6stl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204253-z2q6stl","updated":"20220906204253"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"系统将写请求交给主数据库处理，读请求交给从数据库处理。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204254-b8gtana","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204254-b8gtana","updated":"20220906204254"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"落实到项目本身的话，常用的方式有两种：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204255-u9q2xy0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204255-u9q2xy0","updated":"20220906204255"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"1.代理方式"}]},{"ID":"20220906204256-ixdv512","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204256-ixdv512","updated":"20220906204256"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"代理方式实现读写分离","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/high-performance/read-and-write-separation-and-library-subtable/read-and-write-separation-proxy.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204257-u7fax2t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204257-u7fax2t","updated":"20220906204257"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们可以在应用和数据中间加了一个代理层。应用程序所有的数据请求都交给代理层处理，代理层负责分离读写请求，将它们路由到对应的数据库中。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204258-rujtvks","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204258-rujtvks","updated":"20220906204258"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"提供类似功能的中间件有 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"MySQL Router"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（官方）、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Atlas"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"（基于 MySQL Proxy）、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Maxscale"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"、","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"MyCat"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204259-tm07a1w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204259-tm07a1w","updated":"20220906204259"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"2.组件方式"}]},{"ID":"20220906204260-gqn19hn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204260-gqn19hn","updated":"20220906204260"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在这种方式中，我们可以通过引入第三方组件来帮助我们读写请求。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204261-fshtwzt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204261-fshtwzt","updated":"20220906204261"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这也是我比较推荐的一种方式。这种方式目前在各种互联网公司中用的最多的，相关的实际的案例也非常多。如果你要采用这种方式的话，推荐使用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"sharding-jdbc"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，直接引入 jar 包即可使用，非常方便。同时，也节省了很多运维的成本。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204262-o8zjcyz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204262-o8zjcyz","updated":"20220906204262"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你可以在 shardingsphere 官方找到 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://shardingsphere.apache.org/document/legacy/3.x/document/cn/manual/sharding-jdbc/usage/read-write-splitting/","TextMarkTextContent":"sharding-jdbc 关于读写分离的操作"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204263-270s0t6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204263-270s0t6","updated":"20220906204263"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主从复制原理了解么？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204264-bbhk1m7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204264-bbhk1m7","updated":"20220906204264"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"MySQL binlog(binary log 即二进制日志文件) 主要记录了 MySQL 数据库中数据的所有变化(数据库执行的所有 DDL 和 DML 语句)。因此，我们根据主库的 MySQL binlog 日志就能够将主库的数据同步到从库中。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204265-zyf5l1s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204265-zyf5l1s","updated":"20220906204265"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更具体和详细的过程是这个样子的（图片来自于：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://www.toptal.com/mysql/mysql-master-slave-replication-tutorial","TextMarkTextContent":"《MySQL Master-Slave Replication on the Same Machine》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204266-f1dcgs1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204266-f1dcgs1","updated":"20220906204266"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"MySQL主从复制","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/java-guide-blog/78816271d3ab52424bfd5ad3086c1a0f.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204267-5ectwq0","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204267-5ectwq0","updated":"20220906204267"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204268-bpo2v5x","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204268-bpo2v5x","updated":"20220906204268"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204269-615q6iz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204269-615q6iz","updated":"20220906204269"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主库将数据库中数据的变化写入到 binlog","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204270-u7nytua","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204270-u7nytua","updated":"20220906204270"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204271-lpgnif0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204271-lpgnif0","updated":"20220906204271"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从库连接主库","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204272-eqg5515","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204272-eqg5515","updated":"20220906204272"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204273-xzlr86i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204273-xzlr86i","updated":"20220906204273"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从库会创建一个 I/O 线程向主库请求更新的 binlog","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204274-99nase9","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NA==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204274-99nase9","updated":"20220906204274"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204275-x9hst0j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204275-x9hst0j","updated":"20220906204275"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"主库会创建一个 binlog dump 线程来发送 binlog ，从库中的 I/O 线程负责接收","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204276-horqai8","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"5","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":5,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NQ==","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204276-horqai8","updated":"20220906204276"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204277-61mryxi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204277-61mryxi","updated":"20220906204277"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从库的 I/O 线程将接收的 binlog 写入到 relay log 中。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204278-etzfucu","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"6","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":6,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Ng==","Num":6},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204278-etzfucu","updated":"20220906204278"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204279-rjwvvid","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204279-rjwvvid","updated":"20220906204279"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"从库的 SQL 线程读取 relay log 同步数据本地（也就是再执行一遍 SQL ）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204280-qb6tfv2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204280-qb6tfv2","updated":"20220906204280"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"怎么样？看了我对主从复制这个过程的讲解，你应该搞明白了吧!","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204281-tg9yv0z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204281-tg9yv0z","updated":"20220906204281"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你一般看到 binlog 就要想到主从复制。当然，除了主从复制之外，binlog 还能帮助我们实现数据恢复。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204282-5kyykhw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204282-5kyykhw","updated":"20220906204282"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🌈 拓展一下：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204283-4ocqm7l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204283-4ocqm7l","updated":"20220906204283"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不知道大家有没有使用过阿里开源的一个叫做 canal 的工具。这个工具可以帮助我们实现 MySQL 和其他数据源比如 Elasticsearch 或者另外一台 MySQL 数据库之间的数据同步。很显然，这个工具的底层原理肯定也是依赖 binlog。canal 的原理就是模拟 MySQL 主从复制的过程，解析 binlog 将数据同步到其他的数据源。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204284-yxh7cy4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204284-yxh7cy4","updated":"20220906204284"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，像咱们常用的分布式缓存组件 Redis 也是通过主从复制实现的读写分离。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204285-4iwaa45","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204285-4iwaa45","updated":"20220906204285"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"🌕 简单总结一下：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204286-bitt42u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204286-bitt42u","updated":"20220906204286"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"MySQL 主从复制是依赖于 binlog 。另外，常见的一些同步 MySQL 数据到其他数据源的工具（比如 canal）的底层一般也是依赖 binlog 。"}]},{"ID":"20220906204287-p4dcals","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204287-p4dcals","updated":"20220906204287"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分库分表","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204288-vkzx2s7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204288-vkzx2s7","updated":"20220906204288"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读写分离主要应对的是数据库读并发，没有解决数据库存储问题。试想一下：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"如果 MySQL 一张表的数据量过大怎么办?"}]},{"ID":"20220906204289-b3beovf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204289-b3beovf","updated":"20220906204289"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"换言之，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"我们该如何解决 MySQL 的存储压力呢？"}]},{"ID":"20220906204290-f5z02dk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204290-f5z02dk","updated":"20220906204290"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案之一就是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分库分表"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204291-r51znf8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204291-r51znf8","updated":"20220906204291"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何为分库？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204292-90tpm0c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204292-90tpm0c","updated":"20220906204292"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分库"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 就是将数据库中的数据分散到不同的数据库上。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204293-nahedxn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204293-nahedxn","updated":"20220906204293"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面这些操作都涉及到了分库：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204294-f8um2j8","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204294-f8um2j8","updated":"20220906204294"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204295-uqimj3v","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204295-uqimj3v","updated":"20220906204295"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204296-si6mas3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204296-si6mas3","updated":"20220906204296"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你将数据库中的用户表和用户订单表分别放在两个不同的数据库。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204297-fexdw8l","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204297-fexdw8l","updated":"20220906204297"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204298-2nccufu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204298-2nccufu","updated":"20220906204298"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由于用户表数据量太大，你对用户表进行了水平切分，然后将切分后的 2 张用户表分别放在两个不同的数据库。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204299-wpm3xx6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204299-wpm3xx6","updated":"20220906204299"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"何为分表？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204300-y3qumoo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204300-y3qumoo","updated":"20220906204300"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分表"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 就是对单表的数据进行拆分，可以是垂直拆分，也可以是水平拆分。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204301-jq4e3h8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204301-jq4e3h8","updated":"20220906204301"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"何为垂直拆分？"}]},{"ID":"20220906204302-of10h5y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204302-of10h5y","updated":"20220906204302"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简单来说，垂直拆分是对数据表列的拆分，把一张列比较多的表拆分为多张表。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204303-xp9ms47","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204303-xp9ms47","updated":"20220906204303"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"举个例子：我们可以将用户信息表中的一些列单独抽出来作为一个表。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204304-f312vuo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204304-f312vuo","updated":"20220906204304"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"何为水平拆分？"}]},{"ID":"20220906204305-0my74c8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204305-0my74c8","updated":"20220906204305"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简单来说，水平拆分是对数据表行的拆分，把一张行比较多的表拆分为多张表。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204306-qdobb3p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204306-qdobb3p","updated":"20220906204306"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"举个例子：我们可以将用户信息表拆分成多个用户信息表，这样就可以避免单一表数据量过大对性能造成影响。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204307-b8wkya8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204307-b8wkya8","updated":"20220906204307"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://time.geekbang.org/column/intro/100006601?code=i00Nq3pHUcUj04ZWy70NCRl%2FD2Lfj8GVzcGzZ3Wf5Ug%3D","TextMarkTextContent":"《从零开始学架构》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 中的有一张图片对于垂直拆分和水平拆分的描述还挺直观的。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204308-dtv5j3w","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204308-dtv5j3w","updated":"20220906204308"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/java-guide-blog/662ea3bda90061d0b40177e3a46fefc3.jpg","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204309-d2f8tpa","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204309-d2f8tpa","updated":"20220906204309"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"什么情况下需要分库分表？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204310-92hdcsp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204310-92hdcsp","updated":"20220906204310"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"遇到下面几种场景可以考虑分库分表：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204311-eebpqpn","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204311-eebpqpn","updated":"20220906204311"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204312-hzubvml","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204312-hzubvml","updated":"20220906204312"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204313-rd21b3f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204313-rd21b3f","updated":"20220906204313"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"单表的数据达到千万级别以上，数据库读写速度比较缓慢（分表）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204314-olukofw","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204314-olukofw","updated":"20220906204314"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204315-ufe80fh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204315-ufe80fh","updated":"20220906204315"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据库中的数据占用的空间越来越大，备份时间越来越长（分库）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204316-lbx18u3","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204316-lbx18u3","updated":"20220906204316"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204317-9xvigz5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204317-9xvigz5","updated":"20220906204317"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"应用的并发量太大（分库）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204318-ygdj8iv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204318-ygdj8iv","updated":"20220906204318"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分库分表会带来什么问题呢？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204319-0udljl8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204319-0udljl8","updated":"20220906204319"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"记住，你在公司做的任何技术决策，不光是要考虑这个技术能不能满足我们的要求，是否适合当前业务场景，还要重点考虑其带来的成本。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204320-4m8sf15","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204320-4m8sf15","updated":"20220906204320"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"引入分库分表之后，会给系统带来什么挑战呢？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204321-1bpmjj6","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204321-1bpmjj6","updated":"20220906204321"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204322-w7g67b1","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204322-w7g67b1","updated":"20220906204322"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204323-dpsfqvk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204323-dpsfqvk","updated":"20220906204323"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"join 操作"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ： 同一个数据库中的表分布在了不同的数据库中，导致无法使用 join 操作。这样就导致我们需要手动进行数据的封装，比如你在一个数据库中查询到一个数据之后，再根据这个数据去另外一个数据库中找对应的数据。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204324-m4w17mv","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204324-m4w17mv","updated":"20220906204324"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204325-namghgn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204325-namghgn","updated":"20220906204325"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"事务问题"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：同一个数据库中的表分布在了不同的数据库中，如果单个操作涉及到多个数据库，那么数据库自带的事务就无法满足我们的要求了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204326-31e012j","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204326-31e012j","updated":"20220906204326"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204327-v19fbtl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204327-v19fbtl","updated":"20220906204327"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分布式 id"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：分库之后， 数据遍布在不同服务器上的数据库，数据库的自增主键已经没办法满足生成的主键唯一了。我们如何为不同的数据节点生成全局唯一主键呢？这个时候，我们就需要为我们的系统引入分布式 id 了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204328-er68oxm","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204328-er68oxm","updated":"20220906204328"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204329-h7xvdo5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204329-h7xvdo5","updated":"20220906204329"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"......","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204330-lf0ce8n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204330-lf0ce8n","updated":"20220906204330"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，引入分库分表之后，一般需要 DBA 的参与，同时还需要更多的数据库服务器，这些都属于成本。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204331-a75mdoj","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204331-a75mdoj","updated":"20220906204331"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分库分表有没有什么比较推荐的方案？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204332-7vv2e5n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204332-7vv2e5n","updated":"20220906204332"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ShardingSphere 项目（包括 Sharding-JDBC、Sharding-Proxy 和 Sharding-Sidecar）是当当捐入 Apache 的，目前主要由京东数科的一些巨佬维护。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204333-qo0k2hk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204333-qo0k2hk","updated":"20220906204333"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/img_convert/60649996bfc69acb1953063dddf0c2e6.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204334-nfpxr7b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204334-nfpxr7b","updated":"20220906204334"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ShardingSphere 绝对可以说是当前分库分表的首选！ShardingSphere 的功能完善，除了支持读写分离和分库分表，还提供分布式事务、数据库治理等功能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204335-2olqzsn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204335-2olqzsn","updated":"20220906204335"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，ShardingSphere 的生态体系完善，社区活跃，文档完善，更新和发布比较频繁。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204336-z7vlkq8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204336-z7vlkq8","updated":"20220906204336"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"艿艿之前写了一篇分库分表的实战文章，各位朋友可以看看：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/A2MYOFT7SP-7kGOon8qJaw","TextMarkTextContent":"《芋道 Spring Boot 分库分表入门》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204337-0qmrmrq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204337-0qmrmrq","updated":"20220906204337"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分库分表后，数据怎么迁移呢？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204338-9w06wc6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204338-9w06wc6","updated":"20220906204338"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分库分表之后，我们如何将老库（单库单表）的数据迁移到新库（分库分表后的数据库系统）呢？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204339-blal8eh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204339-blal8eh","updated":"20220906204339"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"比较简单同时也是非常常用的方案就是","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"停机迁移"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，写个脚本老库的数据写到新库中。比如你在凌晨 2 点，系统使用的人数非常少的时候，挂一个公告说系统要维护升级预计 1 小时。然后，你写一个脚本将老库的数据都同步到新库中。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204340-0m3yfi7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204340-0m3yfi7","updated":"20220906204340"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果你不想停机迁移数据的话，也可以考虑","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"双写方案"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。双写方案是针对那种不能停机迁移的场景，实现起来要稍微麻烦一些。具体原理是这样的：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204341-uy2dxqy","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204341-uy2dxqy","updated":"20220906204341"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204342-uxwajsb","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204342-uxwajsb","updated":"20220906204342"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204343-ypd93fm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204343-ypd93fm","updated":"20220906204343"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们对老库的更新操作（增删改），同时也要写入新库（双写）。如果操作的数据不存在于新库的话，需要插入到新库中。 这样就能保证，咱们新库里的数据是最新的。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204344-6m2go98","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204344-6m2go98","updated":"20220906204344"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204345-0d9ma31","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204345-0d9ma31","updated":"20220906204345"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在迁移过程，双写只会让被更新操作过的老库中的数据同步到新库，我们还需要自己写脚本将老库中的数据和新库的数据做比对。如果新库中没有，那咱们就把数据插入到新库。如果新库有，旧库没有，就把新库对应的数据删除（冗余数据清理）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204346-1mws1ho","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204346-1mws1ho","updated":"20220906204346"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204347-61acx9f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204347-61acx9f","updated":"20220906204347"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"重复上一步的操作，直到老库和新库的数据一致为止。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204348-k1hddj9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204348-k1hddj9","updated":"20220906204348"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"想要在项目中实施双写还是比较麻烦的，很容易会出现问题。我们可以借助上面提到的数据库同步工具 Canal 做增量数据迁移（还是依赖 binlog，开发和维护成本较低）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204349-erj12km","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906204349-erj12km","updated":"20220906204349"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"总结","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906204350-5w18m65","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204350-5w18m65","updated":"20220906204350"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204351-o9motc9","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204351-o9motc9","updated":"20220906204351"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204352-d9d8aon","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204352-d9d8aon","updated":"20220906204352"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读写分离主要是为了将对数据库的读写操作分散到不同的数据库节点上。 这样的话，就能够小幅提升写性能，大幅提升读性能。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204353-7n13fbh","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204353-7n13fbh","updated":"20220906204353"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204354-wego6ww","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204354-wego6ww","updated":"20220906204354"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"读写分离基于主从复制，MySQL 主从复制是依赖于 binlog 。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204355-z4idwru","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204355-z4idwru","updated":"20220906204355"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204356-kt766k2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204356-kt766k2","updated":"20220906204356"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分库"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 就是将数据库中的数据分散到不同的数据库上。","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分表"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 就是对单表的数据进行拆分，可以是垂直拆分，也可以是水平拆分。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204357-s5ck9ar","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204357-s5ck9ar","updated":"20220906204357"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204358-m81r9pp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204358-m81r9pp","updated":"20220906204358"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"引入分库分表之后，需要系统解决事务、分布式 id、无法 join 操作问题。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906204359-rx4jrou","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906204359-rx4jrou","updated":"20220906204359"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906204360-t8ozsym","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906204360-t8ozsym","updated":"20220906204360"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"ShardingSphere 绝对可以说是当前分库分表的首选！ShardingSphere 的功能完善，除了支持读写分离和分库分表，还提供分布式事务、数据库治理等功能。另外，ShardingSphere 的生态体系完善，社区活跃，文档完善，更新和发布比较频繁。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]}]}